TopicTitle: No MechJeb Tab or Parts Showing Up

Articles.Content:
As the title says, I've been unable to get the tab or any of the parts to show up.

I've tried the following:

-Fresh install on my G Drive
-Moving the install to my H Drive
-Installing it manually (while deleting all other mods i.e mechjeb being the only mod installed)
-Installing it using CKAN while it also being the only mod
-Trying the dev version via CKAN while it also being the only mod
-I tested each iteration/attempt in sandbox mode
-Deleting the game completely and installing it via CKAN as the only mod (This will be the install of the output log I post).

https://github.com/MuMech/MechJeb2/files/1272587/output_log.txt

Edit: Also tried the dev version on my fresh install. Still a no go.
